data.description: Beautifully maintained and thoughtfully designed home located perfectly on Cul de Sac in Copper Basin. Custom moldings, extensive woodwork and carefully chosen updates make this stunning home ready to move in.  Hardwood floors greet you at the entry with double doors leading to office/den.  The focal point fireplace anchors the great room as it flows directly to kitchen outfitted with granite island, SS appliances, generous pantry and kitchen sink overlooking garden spaces with charming wood shutters. Dining area is adjacent to covered patio that leads to additional outdoor entertainment space and a gardener’s paradise curated in planting beds, shed and custom mini greenhouse. Large primary bedroom on the main level with generous windows and trayed ceiling. Upstairs 2 bedrooms, loft w/ extensive study area and bonus room with storage can be used as a 4th bedroom. Garage 4th car bay separated into shop area – can easily be converted back.
